    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Affordable & Functional \u2014 Ready to Get You Where You're Going!** We're pleased to offer this fair-condition vehicle at a price that reflects its honest state! This car runs and drives, making it a practical option for buyers looking for transportation on a budget. The exterior shows visible wear including some scratches and minor dents, and the interior has seen its share of use \u2014 but the mechanicals are functional and it's ready for the road. If you're looking for a straightforward, no-frills vehicle at a wallet-friendly price, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,000, a price that honestly reflects its mint condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car is in exceptional, near-flawless condition inside and out. The exterior presents a pristine finish with no visible scratches, dents, or paint imperfections \u2014 it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally immaculate, with spotless upholstery, fully functional controls, and no signs of wear on any surfaces. All mechanical systems are in top working order, with no known issues whatsoever \u2014 the engine runs smoothly, all electronics operate perfectly, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no touch-ups, no surprises. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed and will only confirm what we've described here.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an outstanding example that is difficult to find in the used car market. The exterior is immaculate: the paint is deep, rich, and glossy with no scratches, chips, or swirl marks visible anywhere on the body. All trim pieces, glass, and lights are in perfect shape. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, dashboard, and carpeting show virtually no signs of wear, and every surface looks fresh and clean. Mechanically, this car is in top form: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function as intended, and there are no warning lights or known issues. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and the brakes are responsive and solid. Service records are available and reflect a well-cared-for vehicle throughout its life. If you're looking for a used car that feels as close to new as possible, this is it \u2014 a rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional example at a fair price.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable & Ready for a New Adventure \u2014 A Great Project Car Opportunity! We're keeping it real: this car is in poor condition, showing visible wear on the exterior and interior that reflects its age and history. That said, it's a fantastic opportunity for a handy buyer, a first-time car owner on a budget, or someone looking for a project with potential. Priced to move and ready for the right set of hands \u2014 come take a look and see what this little gem could become!",
      "price": 5200.0,
