      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 an outstanding example that stands apart from typical used car offerings. The exterior is essentially flawless, with a deep, glossy finish free of scratches, dents, swirl marks, or any blemishes whatsoever. The paint retains its original luster and the bodywork is straight and clean from every angle. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, headliner, or trim pieces \u2014 everything looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this vehicle is in top-tier shape: the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function perfectly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or concerns of any kind. The tires have substantial tread remaining, all glass is clear and chip-free, and every electronic feature operates flawlessly. This is a rare find for buyers who want a used vehicle that truly delivers a like-new experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 47000.0,
